OL,4,CWiltshire pub's new chalet 'breaks
OL,5,CCovid rules'
OL,6, A "livid" pub landlord says he has
OL,7, spent #50,000 on a chalet for outside
OL,8, dining only to be told a week before
OL,9, opening it contravenes Covid-19 rules.
OL,11,FJason Kalen, who runs The Marlborough
OL,12,Fin Wiltshire, fitted a bar, pizza oven
OL,13,Fand a TV in the wooden structure.
OL,15,FHe said he followed Wiltshire Council's
OL,16,Fadvice to comply with the regulations.
OL,18,FBut it said government guidance had not
OL,19,Fchanged and outdoor roofed structures
OL,20,Fhad to have at least 50% of their walls
OL,21,Fopen when in use, which his did not.
